Package: mapmisc
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for Producing Maps 
Version: 1.8.1
Date: 2021-04-20
Depends: sp, raster, R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: methods, grDevices, stats, utils, graphics
Suggests: RColorBrewer, classInt, rgdal, rgeos, geosphere, knitr, markdown
Enhances: tools, geonames, XML
Author: Patrick Brown <patrick.brown@utoronto.ca> 
Maintainer: Patrick Brown <patrick.brown@utoronto.ca>
Description: A minimal, light-weight set of tools for producing nice looking maps in R, with support for map projections.  For details see Brown (2016) <doi:10.32614/RJ-2016-005>.
License: GPL
